{
  "stem": "11179.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Didn't pay them money or in anything else and told them, help yourself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And all that stuff-- canned food, uniforms, clothing, all kinds, men, even women clothing-- everything was being sold on the street for next to nothing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everybody had a ball.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Japanese didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And until the Chinese troops came in, American troops came in, and Chinese troops came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Officially, the Chinese troops came in for face saving device for the Chiang Kai-shek.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Of course, they had to let the Chinese troops in first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But American troops were there too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They did not occupy the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They just-- they just occupied certain-- certain areas-- the bases, especially where the Japanese used to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they evacu-- it was also the job of the American ships to evacuate the Japanese back to Japan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Meanwhile, they had them work there tearing down the bunkers they had built on the harbors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I worked for the Army at the time at the port command-- American port command.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we built fences for-- for the Chinese 12th army at that time, to be sent north to fight the Communists.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I've never heard of a battle being fought there, and I have a pretty good guess what happened to those soldiers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They turned around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were treated very badly by their officers, which I witnessed because I was in those warehouses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We-- we put them-- we built those fences so they went on the LSDs where they shipped them, where they shipped north, with all I knew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were equipped by American-- by the American army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they were-- they sprayed them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They didn't want-- whatever, any-- any-- any-- any-- any lice or whatever those people may have had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were a poor bunch of people, in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
